messages.message:
Heads up team, we’ve been having Cypress CI issues lately, which are blocking PRs from being merged. We have disabled these tests for now until the issue is resolved.

*If your PR is blocked by the “Cypress Tests” Github workflow, please rebase on the lastest master.*

Let us know if there’s any issues or questions in this thread or via <!subteam^S07855GV3GV>. Thread (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/CSY11CK7T/p1723668151437939?thread_ts=1723658164.045079&cid=CSY11CK7T)
